            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/cookie.webp",
            "title": "Cookie Questions",
            "content": "<p><strong>What makes Mr.B's Cookies Different? </strong></p><p>Our cookies are made in small batches using browned butter, premium chocolate, and high-quality ingredients. They're thick, soft-baked, and crafted for flavour. Every batch is made with care, consistency, and intention. </p><p><strong>How big are our cookies? </strong></p><p>Our cookies are large, bakery-style cookies - generously portioned and designed to be rich, soft and satisfying. </p><p><strong>Are your cookies baked fresh? </strong></p><p>Yes. All cookies are baked fresh for each order week - never frozen, never sitting on shelves. </p><p><strong>Do you use preservatives? </strong></p><p>No. Our cookies are made without preservatives. For best quality, enjoy them fresh or store properly (see storage tips below). </p><p><strong>How should I store my cookies? </strong></p><p>Keep cookies in an airtight container at room temperature for up to 3 days. For longer storage, refrigeration or freeze and warm slightly before enjoying.</p>"
          }
        },
