            "content": "<p><strong>How does ordering work?</strong></p><p>Orders are placed through our website only. Each week has a limited number of boxes available to ensure quality and freshness. </p><p><strong>Is there an order cutoff?</strong></p><p>Yes. Orders close <strong>Tuesday at midnight </strong>for that weeks bake. Any orders placed after cutoff will roll into the following week. </p><p><strong>Can I change or cancel my order? </strong></p><p>Changes or cancellations must be requested <strong>before the order cutoff. </strong>Once baking begins, all sales are final. </p><p><strong>Do you accept custom orders? </strong></p><p>At this time, we focus on our core and seasonal flavours to maintain consistency and quality.</p>"
          }
        },
