            "content": "<p>Yes! Our cookies make great gifts. You can enter the recipients details at checkout. </p><p><strong>Do you include gift notes?</strong></p><p>Not yet - but gift-ready packaging is always included. Handwritten notes may be added in future releases. </p><p><strong>Do prices include receipts in the box?</strong></p><p>No. Receipts are sent digitally only.</p>"
