            "content": "<p><strong>Do you deliver locally?</strong></p><p>Yes. Local delivery is available in Calgary through our delivery partner. Delivery windows are listed at checkout. </p><p><strong>Do you ship across Canada?</strong></p><p>Yes - Canada-wide shipping is available on select products. Shipping rates are calculated at checkout. </p><p><strong>How are cookies packaged for shipping? </strong></p><p>Cookies are carefully packed and sealed to maintain freshness during transit. However, once shipped, we cannot guarantee condition due to carrier handling. </p><p><strong>Are shipping orders refundable?</strong></p><p>Due to the perishable nature or baked goods, shipped orders are final sale.</p>"
